2) Search for documents where depHead and empId are same
  POST /office_department/_search
  {
    "_source": "employees.empName", 
    
    "query": {
      
      "multi_match": {
        "query": 105,
        "fields": ["DeptHead","employees.empId"]
      }
      
    }
  }
  //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
